channel.title: Victorious317 | Dedi | Most advanced custom RSPS
channel.description:
[CENTER][IMG]http://i.imgur.com/BMvnxgl.png[/img]
Victorious317 was solely made to improve todays genre of "customs" servers. Having to experience tons of servers coming out with non-animated monsters such as Pikachu's, Spongebob's & Luigi's that do not belong in any RSPS, we have decided to make our own to get rid of those servers. We hope to attract all those people to join our server so that those type's of servers die out. We have come up with a system where no matter what type of player you are, you will have the same chance on getting a "custom" item. With our system, there will be a neat market between Skillers & those who like to kill monsters or players. Though there is a chance this may not succeed, we are thankful to have about 10 bug testers along with our team of developers. We hope to surprise you all with a great experience playing our server. We are not seeking for perfection but to see our players enjoy the server with their fellow friends & hopefully create more while they're with us.
[B][IMG]http://i.imgur.com/oY9tN5O.png[/img] [URL=http://"http://victorious317.com/"]Website[/URL] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/lierFbu.png[/img] [URL=http://"http://victorious317.com/"]Forums[/URL] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/cmvuzIG.png[/img] [URL=http://"https://www.dropbox.com/s/0wcshobsokmk390/VictoriousV1.1.jar?dl=1"]Download[/URL][/B]
[B]Note: Our website is currently down because apparently we are a big competition to a server with 100+ players.[/B]
[IMG]http://i.imgur.com/gxpjyAF.png[/img]
- OSRS Bosses & Items - PvP System; Pk Point Shop, Wilderness Activity Points, In-Game PvP Highscores - Skilling: Skilling Point Shop, All Skills Except Hunter, Dungeoneering, Construction & Summoning - Boss Pets - Custom Home - Crystal Keys System - Zooming In & Out - 25+ Achievements - Recoloring Completionist Cape - Recoloring Whip & Dark Bow System - Boss Kill Log - Dicing & Flower Poker
[B] [COLOR="#00FF00"]- Special Points System for Normal Players - Get 500 Points & you can get free donator rank - Customs Box System - You can get it from Pking, PvMing (Kill Bosses), Skilling (get 99 in a skill [except from combat]) & Slayer[/B]
